          "title": "depends: build miniupnpc with CMake",
          "body": "This picks up one of the changes from #29232, which is a switch to building miniupnpc with CMake. It includes an update to the most recent version of miniupnpc (2.2.7), which means we can drop one patch from that commit, and includes a new patch for a change I've upstreamed https://github.com/miniupnp/miniupnp/pull/721, as well as some suggestions from the previous PR.\r\n\r\nAs part of this change we move cmake-minimal in Guix into the global package set.\r\n\r\nBased on #29706.",
